{"tid":792262,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"隻90後fg比我玩到狗咁","createTime":"2018-08-24T12:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T13:57:02.000Z","uid":36143,"like":11,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9d20d20bbf66a863b468b44d169fa5339c34b42d","tid":792262,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"話說小妹做hr<br />\n<br />\n咁都會幫公司開啲假位扮請人(實情攞料玩人)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁最近就寫左個post請個aisstant mamager, 開30k(會壓到得20k,反正唔請的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n咁有隻90後話自己Oxford graduate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (一聽就知啲嘢雞大專)<br />\n<br />\n咪叫佢黎玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知黎度居然話I dont know Chinese<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻用英文話番佢 you no know Chinese come do what 7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢個樣都聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好心英文甘廢就考左個ieits先黎見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我扮話即刻有消息，叫佢等等(實情小妹去左柯屎同下午茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n後尾第左兩個鐘先話唔請佢叫佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8781a68e79ac919ae76872bf7085cd0832e00761","tid":792262,"uid":136617,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:08:37.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"bf63b767f1ac1399eb15882cec24090517d0e85e","tid":792262,"uid":144127,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"0分"},{"pid":"9559667008d23f79191c0c99ee3632840350cca1","tid":792262,"uid":61420,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T12:09:01.000Z","msg